Chamerstrasse 176 6300 Zug

Switzerland 

SWISH is the ultimate choice for a luxury lifestyle. It serves as a powerful symbol that reverberates with clientele, all under one prestigious brand. It’s an honor to shape our perceptions, influence our choices and become an integral part of peoples’ lives. As the pioneering force in introducing luxury bath-ware and kitchenware to the market, we have surpassed boundaries and established a global presence.

Where Luxury Lifestyle Unfolds

Luxury Building Materials Under A Single Brand

Global Hub

China

SWISH is already in the venture to expand and diversify its product line including building materials and many more. From Zug, Switzerland to Foshan, China, the Global Hub is exporting luxurious products globally with 2 production hubs; one in China and another in Turkey, along with 2 sales hubs in UAE and Bangladesh. We took China as our Global Hub because of its high-quality production, availability of best quality ceramic and its geographical location.

Smart City, Foshan
Guangdong, China

Brand

A brand is much more than just a logo or a name. It represents the identity and spirit of a company, encapsulating its values, mission and reputation.

Belief

We firmly believe in the power of exclusivity to elevate everyday life. We believe that your living spaces should be a reflection of your unique style, personality and aspirations.

Betterment

Beyond the individual components of a business, success lies in the positive impact a company can make on the world. Betterment represents brand

Production

Hub of SWISH

We believe in factory less manufacturing. Because, in the ever-evolving landscape of modern business, a paradigm shift is underway with the rise of factory-less manufacturing. This innovative approach in our business represents a departure from traditional manufacturing models, focusing on trendy design, with unprecedented opportunities for growth and success.  It also ensures clients keep up with the ever-changing modern lifestyle.

China

Production Hub-1

China is our most significant manufacturing partner since China has 10,000 years history of ceramic and their production process is top class in the whole world.

Turkey

Production Hub-2

Since Turkey has a rich history of producing world class luxury products with European flavours and its geographical location is very significant for SWISH, we took Turkey as another Production Hub. Together, let’s conquer the World!

Advanced

Quality Production

In the journey to be the most valuable Brand in the world, SWISH never compromise with its design, quality and service. We wholeheartedly believe that trend is temporary but class is permanent. As a global brand, we always try to maintain the unique class of our quality delivery, definitely following the trendy designs. 

The Best

Production Hub In The World

Since our vision is to establish SWISH as world’s the most valuable Brand in the arena of lavish finishing products for Luxurious Lifestyle property under a single Brand, we have ensured that our products, which are our core delivery, must be produced in the best factories of the world. This is why, we have chosen China and Turkey as our Production Hubs since these countries are world’s best in the category. And since we like to be the trendsetter in the market as well, we always thrive for excellence and this is why we always keep our eyes wide open to ensure world’s best design and quality.

Sales Hub - 01

UAE Sales Hub

UAE market is very crucial for us since this multicultural land is exceptionally known for its exotic and luxurious lifestyle. As a part of our global expansion, we established a flagship store in Dubai, UAE.

Sales Hub - 02

Bangladesh Sales Hub

Considering the size of population and the market, presently we are running 07 Flagship Stores in Bangladesh.

Upcoming

Sales Hub

For global expansion, at present, SWISH is on the move to explore the markets in Bahrain, Bhutan, Brunei, Cambodia, Kuwait, Nepal, Qatar, Vietnam, and many more to come in the list very soon.

Global

Network

With the vision to establish SWISH as world’s the most valuable Brand in the arena of lavish finishing products for Luxurious Lifestyle property under a single Brand, SWISH has gathered all the top resources and all-out efforts to make this journey a very successful one. We are proudly expanding our business keeping the vision in the core of our unified hearts.
